{
  "_comment": [
    "Template for MCP server configuration.",
    "Copy this file to .mcp.json (which is gitignored) and add any servers you want available to Superagent.",
    "",
    "Superagent itself requires no MCP servers for the quick-start. Each ingestor declares its own MCP / CLI requirements; see superagent/docs/data-sources.md.",
    "",
    "Common personal-life servers you might wire up here:",
    "  - apple-reminders / apple-notes (via osascript)",
    "  - gmail / google-calendar (Google Workspace MCP)",
    "  - apple-health (healthsync SQLite)",
    "  - plaid / monarch / ynab (finance)",
    "  - whoop / strava / oura / garmin (wearables)",
    "  - home-assistant / tesla (smart-home / vehicles)",
    "",
    "Each ingestor probes its required source on first run; missing sources degrade gracefully — they never block other ingestors."
  ],
  "mcpServers": {}
}
